No, listen

00:38:58.560 --> 00:38:59.520
Let me ask you, Dad

00:38:59.920 --> 00:39:01.480
Is it really worth getting this angry?

00:39:01.480 --> 00:39:02.640
You'll just make yourself sick

00:39:03.280 --> 00:39:03.920
Yes

00:39:04.560 --> 00:39:06.640
I dragged Uncle Lin here to make money taking photos

00:39:07.240 --> 00:39:08.760
But who am I making the money for?

00:39:09.080 --> 00:39:10.440
Isn't it for our family?

00:39:10.640 --> 00:39:11.600
In just one week

00:39:11.600 --> 00:39:12.720
I made thirty thousand yuan

00:39:13.000 --> 00:39:14.960
A month easily brings in over a hundred thousand

00:39:15.160 --> 00:39:16.360
How long would you have to scoop paper

00:39:16.360 --> 00:39:17.520
To earn that kind of money?

00:39:17.520 --> 00:39:18.520
Bullshit!

00:39:18.720 --> 00:39:19.720
You're selling out our ancestors

00:39:19.720 --> 00:39:21.000
How much do you think that's worth?

00:39:21.200 --> 00:39:22.560
No, Uncle Lin, look at this

00:39:22.560 --> 00:39:23.880
He's dragging the ancestors out again

00:39:23.880 --> 00:39:25.800
Can the ancestors pay the workers' wages?

00:39:25.840 --> 00:39:26.640
Just answer me this

00:39:26.640 --> 00:39:28.400
If the money's in hand, would you take it?

00:39:28.400 --> 00:39:29.280
I'm gonna beat you to death!

00:39:29.280 --> 00:39:30.280
Old Xuan, Old Xuan, Old Xuan

00:39:30.280 --> 00:39:31.000
It's my fault, my fault

00:39:31.160 --> 00:39:32.040
Old Xuan, don't be angry

00:39:32.120 --> 00:39:34.640
The kid did it all for me

00:39:35.080 --> 00:39:36.240
In his heart

00:39:36.400 --> 00:39:38.400
The Xuan family legacy means nothing

00:39:38.400 --> 00:39:40.520
All he sees is money

00:39:40.960 --> 00:39:42.680
But I did the work too

00:39:42.920 --> 00:39:44.960
Didn't I dry the bark material?

00:39:45.560 --> 00:39:47.080
Look, see for yourself

00:39:47.080 --> 00:39:48.360
Fine, let's take a look

00:39:53.440 --> 00:39:54.240
Take a look.

00:39:54.520 --> 00:39:56.080
This is the bark you dried?

00:39:56.440 --> 00:39:58.440
What's the key to drying bark?

00:39:58.640 --> 00:40:00.000
Haven't I told you before?

00:40:03.360 --> 00:40:04.360
Two pieces shouldn't touch.

00:40:05.160 --> 00:40:06.160
Stones shouldn't face the sky.

00:40:07.480 --> 00:40:08.640
Damn it.

00:40:08.720 --> 00:40:10.040
You actually remembered?

00:40:10.840 --> 00:40:14.400
Airflow and sunlight make good bark.

00:40:14.440 --> 00:40:15.880
What is this you've dried?

00:40:16.600 --> 00:40:17.520
Just look at it.

00:40:18.080 --> 00:40:19.480
It's all rotten.

00:40:19.800 --> 00:40:20.680
Eight months from now,

00:40:20.680 --> 00:40:22.240
This will all be a pile of trash.

00:40:22.240 --> 00:40:23.800
You think you can dry good bark?

00:40:23.840 --> 00:40:24.880
Make good paper?

00:40:28.840 --> 00:40:30.400
Look at this, Old Lin.

00:40:30.720 --> 00:40:32.720
What kind of people did you hire?

00:40:33.280 --> 00:40:35.880
Trampling all over my bark.

00:40:36.080 --> 00:40:37.120
Can't you see?

00:40:38.160 --> 00:40:39.440
Don't step on that!

00:40:40.920 --> 00:40:41.720
Old Lin.

00:40:42.400 --> 00:40:45.040
He doesn't get it, but you do.

00:40:45.040 --> 00:40:45.840
Old Xuan.

00:40:46.320 --> 00:40:47.800
It's my fault. My fault.

00:40:47.800 --> 00:40:49.880
Making paper is like being a person.

00:40:50.000 --> 00:40:52.520
108 steps, none can be skipped.

00:40:52.960 --> 00:40:53.840
But you, on the other hand,

00:40:55.120 --> 00:40:56.720
All you see is quick money.

00:40:57.040 --> 00:40:59.160
The Xuan family's reputation

00:40:59.160 --> 00:41:00.680
And a papermaker's conscience,

00:41:00.680 --> 00:41:02.600
You've trampled them all underfoot.

00:41:03.080 --> 00:41:03.880
Now hurry up

00:41:04.120 --> 00:41:05.600
And chase all these people out!

00:41:05.600 --> 00:41:06.800
And in that little courtyard,

00:41:06.800 --> 00:41:08.400
That, that loudspeaker thing,

00:41:08.560 --> 00:41:09.640
Get rid of all of it!

00:41:09.920 --> 00:41:10.840
If you don't listen to me,

00:41:11.000 --> 00:41:12.080
I won't let you off.

00:41:15.200 --> 00:41:16.680
Don't, don't be angry, Old Xuan.

00:41:16.680 --> 00:41:18.000
This is all on me.

00:41:27.120 --> 00:41:28.120
What your father said

00:41:29.840 --> 00:41:30.960
Makes a lot of sense.

00:41:32.000 --> 00:41:34.000
This is all Uncle Lin's fault.

00:41:35.320 --> 00:41:36.080
No.

00:41:37.080 --> 00:41:39.480
Uncle Lin, I'm sorry.

00:41:40.320 --> 00:41:41.400
This isn't your fault.

00:41:42.320 --> 00:41:43.000
It's mine.

00:41:46.640 --> 00:41:48.600
Stop filming. Still filming?

00:41:50.440 --> 00:41:51.200
Remember this.

00:41:52.040 --> 00:41:54.520
First scoop, water close to you.

00:41:55.000 --> 00:41:57.320
Second scoop, water breaks center.

00:41:58.120 --> 00:41:59.520
This feel in the hands,

00:42:00.080 --> 00:42:03.000
And the skill of the heart are subtly linked.

00:42:03.880 --> 00:42:05.680
The feel takes lots of practice.

00:42:05.680 --> 00:42:06.960
And the skill of the heart,

00:42:07.280 --> 00:42:08.080
You have to deeply grasp.

00:42:08.280 --> 00:42:09.400
Understood, Master Ye.

00:42:12.280 --> 00:42:13.360
Your hands are torn up.

00:42:14.920 --> 00:42:15.440
It's nothing.

00:42:19.000 --> 00:42:20.480
This paper-scooping trade,

00:42:20.720 --> 00:42:21.600
What it takes

00:42:22.000 --> 00:42:24.640
Is years and years of slow grind.

00:42:24.720 --> 00:42:26.280
You can't rush it.

00:42:26.640 --> 00:42:27.560
I started late.

00:42:28.400 --> 00:42:30.800
To get good, I have to practice more.

00:42:31.280 --> 00:42:32.040
Master Ye.

00:42:32.520 --> 00:42:35.200
His hands are raw. What ointment works?

00:42:35.320 --> 00:42:36.720
No ointment really helps.

00:42:36.840 --> 00:42:37.800
Try some cortisone.

00:42:38.040 --> 00:42:38.840
Master.

00:42:38.920 --> 00:42:39.720
Let me see.

00:42:43.880 --> 00:42:45.640
Stay out of the water for a couple days.

00:42:45.960 --> 00:42:46.920
He was right just now.

00:42:46.920 --> 00:42:48.320
No ointment really works.

00:42:48.520 --> 00:42:49.880
A few days of rest will do it.

00:42:49.880 --> 00:42:51.080
Okay, thank you, Master.

00:42:52.000 --> 00:42:53.480
What are you doing with that ladder?

00:42:53.480 --> 00:42:55.200
You're old and your back's bad.

00:42:55.200 --> 00:42:56.320
Let the young folks do it.

00:42:57.000 --> 00:42:57.920
Just changing a lightbulb.

00:42:57.920 --> 00:42:58.440
I'm used to it.

